<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink141">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>ekkar ñāḻal ceruntiyoṭu kamaḻat</l>
<l>tuvalait taṇṭuḷi vīcip</l>
<l>pacalai ceytaṉa paṉipaṭu tuṟaiyē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
  <l>As Ñāḻal trees on the dunes emit fragrance along with Cerunti trees,</l>
    <l>The ghat upon which dew falls has made [me] pallid </l>
      <l>Having flung sprays of cool drops [of water at me].</l>
</lg>
